---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="West Covina News, City Updates & Local Events | StayJustin"
  description="Stay updated with West Covina news, city hall decisions, new businesses, development projects, traffic updates, and local events."
  canonical="https://www.stayjustin.com/"
>
  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --navy: #123b64;
      --blue: #1f74b7;
      --sky: #dff1fb;
      --gold: #f0b544;
      --orange: #e38b2f;
      --green: #2f8f69;
      --green-dark: #217457;
      --text: #17212b;
      --muted: #5d6b78;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --bg: #f5f8fb;
      --border: #d9e3ec;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(18, 59, 100, 0.10);
      --radius: 18px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eef6fb 0%, #f7fafc 220px, var(--bg) 100%);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      background: rgba(10, 28, 48, 0.88);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      min-height: 76px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .brand-title {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 48px;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), #0d90df);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .btn-green {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-dark));
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero-wrap {
      padding: 28px 0 18px;
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .hero-media {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 430px;
      background: #dbe7f0;
    }

    .hero-media img {
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .hero-media::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(8,20,35,0.08) 0%, rgba(8,20,35,0.00) 55%, rgba(255,255,255,0.30) 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-content {
      padding: 48px 42px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 18px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(240,181,68,0.18), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom left, rgba(31,116,183,0.12), transparent 36%),
        #fff;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      width: fit-content;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: rgba(31,116,183,0.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,116,183,0.18);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .accent { color: var(--blue); }

    .hero-copy {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .hero-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 14px 0 8px;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      margin: 10px 0 18px;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-sub {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .snapshot-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .snapshot-card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--navy), #235d8e);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      min-height: 170px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .snapshot-card.green { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1f8b70, #20795f); }
    .snapshot-card.gold { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d79a2d, #bb7f18); }
    .snapshot-card.light { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2e83c5, #255f99); }

    .snapshot-label {
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .snapshot-title {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 12px 0 8px;
    }

    .snapshot-copy {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .updates-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card-image {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #d8e6f1;
    }

    .card-image img {
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.35s ease;
    }

    .card:hover .card-image img {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .card-tag {
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .card-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      line-height: 1.18;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .card-text {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .card-link {
      margin-top: auto;
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .feature {
      margin-top: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.95), rgba(232,245,255,0.92));
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .feature-copy h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .feature-copy p {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .service-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .service {
      background: rgba(31,116,183,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(31,116,183,0.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .feature-image {
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 360px;
      background: #dceaf4;
    }

    .feature-image img {
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .subscribe {
      margin: 24px 0 40px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d355a, #1564a4);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .subscribe h3 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .subscribe p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      font-size: 1.04rem;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 10px 0 34px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero,
      .feature,
      .subscribe,
      .updates-grid,
      .snapshot-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .updates-grid .card:last-child {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }

      .service-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 14px 0;
      }

      .nav-links {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero,
      .feature,
      .subscribe,
      .updates-grid,
      .snapshot-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-media {
        min-height: 280px;
      }

      .hero-content,
      .feature {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .service-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .section-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .subscribe {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .subscribe .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 20px));
      }

      .brand-title {
        font-size: 1.55rem;
      }

      .brand-sub {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .snapshot-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .card-title {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
      }

      .service-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-title">StayJustin</div>
        <div class="brand-sub">West Covina news • community updates • local tech help</div>
      </div>

      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#updates">News</a>
        <a href="#snapshot">West Covina</a>
        <a href="#tech-help">Tech Help</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Subscribe</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero-wrap">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
          <div class="hero-media">
            <img src="/images/wc-downtown.jpg" alt="A view across West Covina with the San Gabriel Mountains in the distance" />
          </div>

          <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="eyebrow">For neighbors who want the real story</span>
            <h1>What’s Going On in <span class="accent">West Covina</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">Local updates, city meeting takeaways, development news, and everyday community information written the way a neighbor would explain it — clearly, honestly, and without all the extra noise.</p>

            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Subscribe</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#updates">Read Latest Updates</a>
            </div>

            <p class="hero-note">This city matters. The people here matter. And if we stop paying attention and stop showing up for each other, we’re going to lose something special.</p>
            <p class="hero-note">I live here too. I care about what happens here, and I know a lot of good people do too.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="snapshot">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">What’s Happening This Week</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">A quick look at the city meetings, community items, and local updates that stand out right now.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="snapshot-grid">
          <article class="snapshot-card light">
            <div>
              <div class="snapshot-label">Tuesday, March 24</div>
              <div class="snapshot-title">Planning Commission Meeting</div>
            </div>
            <p class="snapshot-copy"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> This is where development decisions begin. What gets discussed here can shape housing, business activity, and how parts of the city grow over time.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="snapshot-card green">
            <div>
              <div class="snapshot-label">Wednesday, March 25</div>
              <div class="snapshot-title">Community &amp; Senior Center Commission</div>
            </div>
            <p class="snapshot-copy"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> These meetings affect programs and services that many residents, seniors, and families depend on.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="snapshot-card gold">
            <div>
              <div class="snapshot-label">Community Event</div>
              <div class="snapshot-title">Couples Connect Workshop</div>
            </div>
            <p class="snapshot-copy"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Events like this help keep the city feeling like a real community, not just a place where people happen to live.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="snapshot-card">
            <div>
              <div class="snapshot-label">Local Business</div>
              <div class="snapshot-title">Mayor’s Restaurant &amp; Business Recognition</div>
            </div>
            <p class="snapshot-copy"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Local businesses give the city its character. When they are supported, the whole community benefits.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="updates">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">What I’m Watching</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">A few local things worth paying attention to right now.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="updates-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/wc-cityhall.jpg" alt="West Covina City Hall" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-tag">City Hall</div>
              <h3 class="card-title">Planning Commission Canceled Tonight</h3>
              <p class="card-text">Sometimes the most useful update is the plain one: what changed, what got canceled, and what people need to know right now.</p>
              <a class="card-link" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read More →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/wc-sign.jpg" alt="West Covina sign at city hall" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-tag">Watch List</div>
              <h3 class="card-title">3 Meetings to Watch This Month</h3>
              <p class="card-text">A clean roundup for the meetings, votes, and decisions worth watching before they quietly pass by.</p>
              <a class="card-link" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read More →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/images/wc-mural.jpg" alt="West Covina mural artwork" />
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-tag">Development</div>
              <h3 class="card-title">What’s Changing Around Downtown</h3>
              <p class="card-text">Use this space to track what’s changing in the city, what’s being built, and what kind of future we’re heading toward.</p>
              <a class="card-link" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read More →</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="tech-help">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-copy">
            <h2>Local <span class="accent">Tech Help</span></h2>
            <p>When something at home stops working, most people do not need a lecture — they need help. This section is for neighbors who want honest, local tech support without the runaround.</p>

            <div class="service-grid">
              <div class="service">Wi-Fi &amp; Internet</div>
              <div class="service">Security Cameras</div>
              <div class="service">Printers &amp; Devices</div>
              <div class="service">Digital Privacy</div>
            </div>

            <a class="btn btn-green" href="mailto:Justin@StayJustin.com?subject=Need%20Tech%20Help">Tell Me What’s Broken</a>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-image">
            <img src="/images/wc-night.jpg" alt="West Covina at night" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="subscribe">
          <div>
            <h3>Subscribe to Just-In Press</h3>
            <p>For the deeper breakdowns, the meeting takeaways, and the context that usually gets lost, subscribe here and stay connected to what’s really happening in West Covina.</p>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://stayjustin.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Subscribe</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div>© 2026 StayJustin</div>
      <div>West Covina updates • Community information • Local tech help</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</MainLayout>
